Usage

FROG_nonpal(my_DNA, pattern1 = "ATGCTGATT", pattern2 = "CGTGACTGGA")

Arguments

my_DNA,

That's your DNAString you aim to digest

pattern1,

The non-PALINDROMIC sequence pattern the restriction enzyme 1 recognizes

pattern2,

OPTIONAL: The non-PALINDROMIC nucleotide sequence pattern the restriction enzyme 2 recognizes

Value

A vector containing fragment lengths

Examples

my_DNA<-gen_DNA(1000)
pattern1<-'ATGCTGATT'
pattern2<-'CGTGACTGGA'
FROG_pal(my_DNA, pattern1, pattern2)
